Interface MASRequest

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    LocalRequest
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuthenticateRequest, MAGInternalRequest, MAGRequestProxy, MASTokenRequest, OAuthTokenRequest, StateRequest

    public interface MASRequest
    An Http Api Request. Instances of this class are immutable.

      • getConnectionListener

        MASConnectionListener getConnectionListener()
        Returns:

      • getResponseBody

        MASResponseBody<?> getResponseBody()
        Returns:
        The response body for this request. The default response body is set to MASResponseBody.byteArrayBody(), you can change the response body to MASResponseBody.jsonBody(), and MASResponseBody.stringBody() or you can implement your own type of response body type.

      • getScope

        java.lang.String getScope()
        Returns:
        The scope for this request. When return null, default scope set (defined in the configuration) will be used.

      • isPublic

        boolean isPublic()
        Returns:
        whether the request is being made outside of primary gateway. When the value is set to true, all automatically injected credentials in SDK will be excluded in the request.

      • notifyOnCancel

        boolean notifyOnCancel()
        Notify the MASCallback.onError(Throwable) when the request is cancelled by MAS.cancelRequest(long).
        Returns:
        True to invoke MASCallback.onError(Throwable) with MAS.RequestCancelledException when the request is cancelled by MAS.cancelRequest(long). Default is false.
